Package: pencal
Title: Penalized Regression Calibration (PRC) for the Dynamic Prediction
    of Survival
Version: 2.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mirko", "Signorelli", , "msignorelli.rpackages@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8102-3356")),
    person("Pietro", "Spitali", role = "ctb"),
    person("Roula", "Tsonaka", role = "ctb"),
    person("Barbara", "Vreede", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Computes penalized regression calibration (PRC), a
    statistical method for the dynamic prediction of survival when many
    longitudinal predictors are available. See Signorelli (2024)
    <doi:10.32614/RJ-2024-014> and Signorelli et al. (2021)
    <doi:10.1002/sim.9178> for details.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://mirkosignorelli.github.io/r
